你生我气了？你把我看成一个脆弱的瓷娃娃

196
00:15:24,323 --> 00:15:27,157
Frank, can I give you a little advice about women?
弗兰克，我能给你一点关于女人的建议吗？

197
00:15:27,159 --> 00:15:28,425
No! Absolutely not!
不！绝对不要！

198
00:15:28,427 --> 00:15:30,260
Listen, you gotta ask yourself,
听我说，你得扪心自问

199
00:15:30,262 --> 00:15:33,097
what is a girl like that doing with a guy like you?
一个姑娘干嘛要跟你这样的家伙混在一起？

200
00:15:33,099 --> 00:15:35,265
It ain't for your looks.
显然不是因为你的长相

201
00:15:35,267 --> 00:15:38,068
You know, I will shoot you. I will shoot you in the liver.
瞧好了，我要给你一枪 给你一枪狠的

202
00:15:39,171 --> 00:15:41,271
A, R, D, A.
A，R，D，A

203
00:15:41,273 --> 00:15:47,077
Adventure, romance, danger, activities you can share as a couple.
