00:16:09,368 --> 00:16:10,934
I'm no crier.
哥是真汉子，才不会哭

210
00:16:17,809 --> 00:16:21,211
Ninety-six hours ago, somebody posted a document on the Internet
96小时前，有人在互联网上发了个帖

211
00:16:21,213 --> 00:16:26,083
that said you and I took part in an operation called Nightshade back in '79.
里面说你和我一同执行了1979年某个名为“夜暮”的行动

212
00:16:26,085 --> 00:16:27,551
That's why you fake died?
你因为这个装的死？

