00:17:20,406 --> 00:17:24,241
Wow. Mommy just slapped Daddy at the dinner table.
哇 西风压倒了东风啊

230
00:17:30,114 --> 00:17:33,050
Is there a human being in the trunk?
后备箱里有人？

231
00:17:33,052 --> 00:17:33,951
Yeah.
对啊

232
00:17:36,221 --> 00:17:37,554
Who is it, Marvin?
是什么人，马文？

233
00:17:39,324 --> 00:17:44,061
He's a Senior Director of Military Intelligence.
是个军情局的高级主管

234
