Do it.
干吧

260
00:19:04,841 --> 00:19:06,041
（香港）

261
00:19:26,030 --> 00:19:27,297
Suit, too.
衣服，也要

262
00:19:31,536 --> 00:19:32,736
Okay, he's clean.
好了，他没问题

263
00:19:41,713 --> 00:19:42,980
Seriously?
不开玩笑？

264
00:19:59,063 --> 00:20:00,764
Sit down, Mr. Han.
坐下，韩先生

265
00:20:13,311 --> 00:20:15,312
Your security is impressive.
你的安保很出色

266
00:20:17,782 --> 00:20:20,150
A business associate.
一个生意伙伴

267
00:20:20,152 --> 00:20:22,786
Julio Alvarez Fernandes.
胡里奥·阿尔瓦雷斯·费尔南德斯

268
00:20:22,788 --> 00:20:26,556
Very diff cult to get close to.
很难接近他

269
00:20:26,558 --> 00:20:30,160
Of course, it must appear like an accident.
当然，必须做得像一场意外事故

270
00:20:30,162 --> 00:20:33,130
Not a problem. Except for one thing.
没问题 除了一件事

271
00:20:33,132 --> 00:20:34,131
Mmm?
嗯？

272
00:20:36,034 --> 00:20:39,436
Mr. Fernandes pays better.
费尔南德斯先生出的价更高

273
00:21:00,691 --> 00:21:02,392
HAN; Yeah?
是？

274
00:21:02,394 --> 00:21:03,693
Who's the target?
目标是谁？

275
00:21:03,695 --> 00:21:05,829
Oh, it's an old pal of yours. Frank Moses.
哦，是你的一个老伙计 弗兰克·摩西

276
00:21:13,504 --> 00:21:15,505
Karma's a bitch, Frank.
你的报应来了，弗兰克

277
00:21:16,406 --> 00:21:18,406
（伦敦-军情六处）

278
00:21:26,150 --> 00:21:27,617
What is this?
出什么事了？

279
00:21:27,619 --> 00:21:29,553
There's a watchword ﬂag on a WikiLeaks document.
在一份网络泄漏的文档里 出现了一个敏感词

280
00:21:29,555 --> 00:21:31,521
It's coded Priority One Alpha Seven.
被编码为 1-A-7 级

281
00:21:32,723 --> 00:21:35,158
- Something called Nightshade. - Shut up!
某个被称为“夜暮”的东西  - 闭嘴！

282
00:21:38,162 --> 00:21:39,229
Get out.
你出去

283
00:21:44,802 --> 00:21:47,104
Find me Victoria Winslow.
给我找到维多利亚·温斯洛

284
00:21:58,149 --> 00:22:00,150
Director Philips?
菲利普主管？

285
00:22:00,152 --> 00:22:02,119
Um...
呃...

286
00:22:02,121 --> 00:22:03,887
I'm with someone right now.
我正陪着某个人呢

287
00:22:13,531 --> 00:22:16,433
Keeping busy, I see.
我看你一直很忙吧

288
00:22:16,435 --> 00:22:18,201
Idle hands do the Devil's work.
下雨天打孩子，闲着也是闲着

289
00:22:21,273 --> 00:22:23,573
Yes.
说的也是

290
00:22:23,575 --> 00:22:26,576
I understand you can get close to Frank Moses.
我明白你跟弗兰克·摩西很熟稔

291
00:22:26,578 --> 00:22:27,911
Yes.
是的

