1206
01:30:30,658 --> 01:30:31,958
What the hell was that?
这是什么鬼东西？

1207
01:30:31,960 --> 01:30:34,227
Blowfish poison.
河豚毒素

1208
01:30:34,229 --> 01:30:37,930
Paralysis and shooting pains will grip your entire body.
麻痹和枪伤引起的痛感 会吞噬你的整个身躯

1209
01:30:37,932 --> 01:30:39,999
And you will slowly asphyxiate until you choke to death
然后你会缓慢地陷入窒息直至死亡

1210
01:30:40,001 --> 01:30:43,536
while remaining fully-conscious, unless you do exactly what I say.
同时神志却完全保持清醒，不想死得这么惨就照我说的去做

1211
01:30:51,812 --> 01:30:54,280
I will die before I compromise my country.
要我背叛我的祖国，我宁可去死

1212
01:30:56,350 --> 01:31:00,486
Okay. We will drive you to your office where you will write a letter on official stationery
好吧，我们会送你去你的办公室，你要在那儿用官方公文写一封信

1213
01:31:00,488 --> 01:31:02,855
denouncing the treatment of women in Iran.
公开谴责伊朗妇女所遭受的歧视

1214
01:31:02,857 --> 01:31:04,023
Then you will get your antidote.
然后你就能拿到解毒剂

1215
01:31:05,425 --> 01:31:06,525
That's it?
我还以为多大事儿呢？

1216
01:31:09,526 --> 01:31:11,126
（伊朗大使馆，伦敦）

1217
01:31:17,037 --> 01:31:18,337
How may I help you?
您有什么事吗？

1218
01:31:18,339 --> 01:31:20,473
我想向伊朗投诚

1219
01:31:36,957 --> 01:31:41,527
Ah. Dr. Bailey, my apologies for the delay.
啊 贝利博士，抱歉耽搁了这么久

1220
01:31:41,529 --> 01:31:44,397
Professor Dombrovski has declared the weapon authentic.
多姆布拉斯基教授已经 验证了该武器的真实性

1221
01:31:44,399 --> 01:31:46,632
And we're prepared to proceed.
我们可以开始启动它了

1222
01:31:46,634 --> 01:31:49,001
As soon as my money's transferred, Mr. Ambassador.
我的钱一到账就动手，大使阁下

1223
01:31:54,441 --> 01:31:56,876
Move! She's with me.
走开！她和我一起的

1224
01:32:17,831 --> 01:32:19,765
Arman?
阿尔曼？

1225
01:32:25,405 --> 01:32:26,539
He needs to go.
叫他离开

1226
01:32:26,541 --> 01:32:27,640
Okay, okay.
好的，好的

1227
01:32:28,843 --> 01:32:30,910
What are you talking about? Who is she?
你说什么？她是谁？

1228
01:32:30,912 --> 01:32:32,945
Sir, I'm sorry, you need 10 leave.
先生，我很抱歉，你得离开此处

1229
01:32:32,947 --> 01:32:33,913
You need to shut up!
你给我闭嘴！

1230
01:32:35,115 --> 01:32:36,382
No.
不要

1231
01:32:36,384 --> 01:32:38,050
What? What is happening here?
怎么了？发生了什么事？

1232
01:32:38,052 --> 01:32:41,520
Sorry. What are you doing?
Tell me what is happening here! Who is she?
告诉我这是怎么回事！她是什么人？

1233
01:32:41,522 --> 01:32:44,357
Get out! When I say "get out," gel out of here!
出去！我说“出去”，你就给我出去！

1234
01:32:44,359 --> 01:32:45,624
You need to go!
你得离开这里！

1235
01:32:45,626 --> 01:32:46,859
You shut the fuck up!
闭上你的鸟嘴！

1236
01:32:56,703 --> 01:32:58,137
Where's the safe?
保险箱在哪儿？

1237
01:32:58,139 --> 01:32:58,938
What?
什么？

1238
01:33:00,140 --> 01:33:01,807
Where's the safe?
保险箱在哪儿？

1239
01:33:13,620 --> 01:33:15,955
Poo pods coming.
一大波粑粑正在接近

1240
01:33:34,408 --> 01:33:36,442
24 Hour Plumbing.
24小时无休管道维修服务

1241
01:33:36,444 --> 01:33:38,744
Hurry. Emergency. Water everywhere. Come quick.
赶紧的 紧急情况 水漫金山啦 快点来啊 

1242
01:33:52,893 --> 01:33:54,894
Stop! Plumbers, wait!
站住！水管工，等等！

1243
01:33:54,896 --> 01:33:56,862
It's okay! This way.
不要紧！这边走

1244
01:33:58,498 --> 01:33:59,965
Money received.
资金已到账

1245
01:33:59,967 --> 01:34:02,001
Good show.
好戏开场了

1246
01:34:02,003 --> 01:34:03,669
Let's see our friend here.
先来看看这边咱们的朋友

1247
01:34:08,508 --> 01:34:09,708
Would you lend me your knife, please?
能把你的刀借给我吗？

1248
01:34:10,710 --> 01:34:12,511
Thank you.
谢谢

1249
01:34:14,081 --> 01:34:15,614
Sorry about the mess on the carpet.
抱歉把地毯弄脏了

1250
01:34:18,118 --> 01:34:19,618
Oh, well.
哦，好了

1251
01:34:19,620 --> 01:34:22,955
At this point, Jack... You don't mind me calling you "Jack," I hope.
都这个时候了，杰克...希望你不会介意我亲切地称呼你“杰克”

1252
01:34:22,957 --> 01:34:25,858
You must be beginning to comprehend
你应该开始从上一次失败的震惊里

1253
01:34:25,860 --> 01:34:28,527
the stunning totality of your failure.
舒缓过来，领悟到些什么了

1254
01:34:30,697 --> 01:34:32,531
You can't give it to them.
你不打算把它交给他们

1255
01:34:32,533 --> 01:34:34,834
Oh, I've no more interest in giving Red Mercury
哦，我既不会把红色水星交给你们

1256
01:34:34,836 --> 01:34:37,536
to these boys than I have in giving it to you.
也更没兴趣交给这些小伙子们

1257
01:34:44,144 --> 01:34:45,511
Jesus.
天啊

1258
01:34:45,513 --> 01:34:47,813
Yes, it's a sad old world, you know.
是啊，世界在悲伤地老去，你也明白

1259
01:34:47,815 --> 01:34:49,648
Anyway, that's only my opinion.
随便了，我想说的就这些

1260
01:34:49,650 --> 01:34:52,685
But the central point is this, Jack,
不过中心思想是这个，杰克

1261
01:34:52,687 --> 01:34:56,822
you see, when men like you and those dickheads from MIG
瞧，比如你，和军情6处的那些鸟人

1262
01:34:56,824 --> 01:34:59,124
or CIA or whatever sewers you came from.
或是中央情报局，或是随便 哪个阴沟里钻出来的人渣

1263
01:34:59,126 --> 01:35:02,595
When you take away not only my life
你们不光消磨了我的青春

1264
01:35:02,597 --> 01:35:06,198
but the innocent lives of my dear beloved wife Natasha
还夺去了我无辜爱妻娜塔莎的生命

1265
01:35:06,200 --> 01:35:08,901
and my little boy, who was only six, you see. Yes.
还有我仅仅6岁的儿子，知道吗

1266
01:35:08,903 --> 01:35:10,069
I mean, what can I say?
我的意思是，我还能说什么呢？

1267
01:35:11,972 --> 01:35:14,707
When you mess with me, buddy,
人若犯我，伙计

1268
01:35:14,709 --> 01:35:16,675
this is what you get.
我必犯人

1269
01:35:16,677 --> 01:35:17,643
Go to hell, old man.
下地狱去吧，老家伙

1270
01:35:24,017 --> 01:35:25,951
Fare thee well, patriot.
永别了您哪，爱国志士

1271
01:35:31,791 --> 01:35:32,958
Boom.
嘭

1272
01:35:34,628 --> 01:35:35,694
Now what's next?
接下来该干啥？

1273
01:35:36,696 --> 01:35:37,796
Ah, Washington.
啊，华盛顿

1274
01:35:50,677 --> 01:35:51,810
Baby, hey'
宝贝，嘿

1275
01:35:53,014 --> 01:35:53,979
Are you okay?
你还好吗？

1276
01:35:56,182 --> 01:35:57,683
Hah!
哈！

1277
01:35:57,685 --> 01:35:58,751
Awesome!
了不起！

1278
01:36:17,003 --> 01:36:18,070
Oh, shit.
哦，该死

1279
01:36:18,072 --> 01:36:20,839
- Is that it? - it's counting down, Frank.
是那个吗？它在倒计时，弗兰克

1280
01:36:20,841 --> 01:36:22,575
Shut it off. Right?
那就关掉它 行吗？

1281
01:36:22,577 --> 01:36:25,644
Shut... Yeah. With what? Acupressure?
关掉...说的轻巧 我用什么关？给它针灸吗？

1282
01:36:25,646 --> 01:36:28,948
- I don't know. - Well, why is it my responsibility?
我怎么知道。好嘛，为什么这成了我的份内事？

1283
01:36:30,016 --> 01:36:31,617
Just do something.
赶紧想想办法

1284
01:36:31,619 --> 01:36:33,919
With my Mr. Chemistry set?
就用我的化学试剂箱？

1285
01:36:35,088 --> 01:36:39,158
I don't know what I'm doing. You want me to push a button?
我不知道该怎么做。你想我随便按个按钮试试？

1286
01:36:39,160 --> 01:36:40,359
Bailey's loose and the bomb's ticking.
贝利行踪不明，炸弹已在倒计时

1287
01:36:45,365 --> 01:36:47,099
Wait. Excuse me, ma'am.
等一等 请原谅，女士

1288
01:36:47,101 --> 01:36:48,634
Hello, I have an appointment.
你好，我有个预约

1289
01:36:51,905 --> 01:36:53,839
Gun!
有枪！

1290
01:37:18,999 --> 01:37:20,099
Gel that bomb outta here.
把炸弹带走

1291
01:37:26,139 --> 01:37:28,140
- Drop it now, darling. That's right. - My gun!
把它扔了，亲爱的 这就对了。我的枪！

1292
01:37:35,281 --> 01:37:36,315
Press the button. Ground floor.
按那个按钮 去地面一层

1293
01:37:37,717 --> 01:37:39,184
Marvin, let's go!
马文，我们走！

1294
01:37:44,825 --> 01:37:46,325
Jolly good show.
大戏热闹开场

1295
01:37:52,999 --> 01:37:53,932
Bollocks.
该死

1296
01:37:59,706 --> 01:38:02,307
You really drive this ridiculous thing?
你就开这么个搞笑的东西出来？

1297
01:38:02,309 --> 01:38:03,676
Can you shoot?
你会开枪不？

1298
01:38:09,916 --> 01:38:11,383
We need eyes, Francis.
我们需要空中追踪，弗兰西斯

1299
01:38:25,031 --> 01:38:26,965
Come on, Frank. Forty minutes.
赶紧的，弗兰克 还有40分钟

1300
01:38:36,209 --> 01:38:37,843
Marvin, how ya doin' back there?
马文，你在后面干什么？

1301
01:38:37,845 --> 01:38:39,344
I can't talk to you right now.
我现在没空说话

1302
01:38:42,483 --> 01:38:44,083
How is it?
怎么样？

1303
01:38:44,085 --> 01:38:45,017
It's fine.
没事

1304
01:38:48,722 --> 01:38:49,822
Shit!
该死！

1305
01:38:54,060 --> 01:38:55,894
Show me something.
秀点能耐出来

1306
01:39:21,454 --> 01:39:23,088
Victoria,
维多利亚

1307
01:39:23,090 --> 01:39:25,257
I got eyes on. Bailey's heading for the M4.
我发现他们了 贝利正向M4行进

1308
01:39:25,259 --> 01:39:26,358
Got it.
收到

1309
01:39:28,394 --> 01:39:29,294
Got it!
找到了！

1310
01:39:30,997 --> 01:39:34,767
This one should stop it and this one should detonate it.
这条应该是停止，而这条应该是引爆

1311
01:39:34,769 --> 01:39:35,934
It's fifty-fifty, Frank.
一半对一半的机会，弗兰克

1312
01:39:38,905 --> 01:39:40,038
Wait!
等等！

1313
01:39:41,941 --> 01:39:44,176
That's weird.
奇怪了

1314
01:39:44,178 --> 01:39:45,210
Do you have any idea what you're doing?
你知道你自己在干什么吗？

1315
01:39:47,847 --> 01:39:50,282
Wait, wait! Wait!
等等，等等！等一下！

1316
01:39:50,284 --> 01:39:51,550
Stop cutting wires!
别再乱剪电线了！

1317
01:39:51,552 --> 01:39:53,352
I knew we were gonna die!
我就知道咱们全都要完蛋！

1318
01:39:56,022 --> 01:39:59,024
- Ready to kill this son of a bitch? Abso-bloody-lutely.
准备好干掉这个混蛋了吗？绝--对--的

1319
01:40:01,394 --> 01:40:02,494
Damn it!
天杀的！

1320
01:40:07,467 --> 01:40:08,934
Trouble.
麻烦了

1321
01:40:08,936 --> 01:40:10,169
Marvin!
马文！

1322
01:40:10,171 --> 01:40:13,272
Frank, it's two pedals and two sticks.
弗兰克，直升机有2套操纵杆和脚舵

1323
01:40:13,274 --> 01:40:14,206
Okay.
好吧

1324
01:40:51,477 --> 01:40:53,979
Damn it! We missed him. He's going into the airport.
该死！我们跟丢了 他往机场去了

1325
01:40:53,981 --> 01:40:55,247
Go get him!
去逮住他！

1326
01:40:55,249 --> 01:40:57,549
- Well, where are you? - In trouble.
- 好吧，你们在哪？ - 仆街中

1327
01:40:57,551 --> 01:41:00,185
Turn back! You are in restricted airspace.
掉转机头！ 你们闯入了禁飞区 

1328
01:41:00,187 --> 01:41:01,854
Frank, they're gonna blow us outta the sky.
弗兰克，他们会在空中把我们轰成渣

1329
01:41:01,856 --> 01:41:03,155
I wouldn't worry about that.
我不想操心那个事

1330
01:41:03,157 --> 01:41:03,989
The engine's shutting down.
引擎正在停止运转

1331
01:41:04,991 --> 01:41:06,558
Mayday! Mayday!
呼叫救助！呼叫救助！

1332
01:41:06,560 --> 01:41:07,893
Frank!
弗兰克！

1333
01:41:09,095 --> 01:41:11,029
I knew we were gonna die!
我就知道我们全都要完蛋！

1334
01:41:11,031 --> 01:41:12,130
This is your last warning!
最后一次警告！

1335
01:41:12,132 --> 01:41:14,967
Oh, please, tell me you're not crashing with a weapon of mass destruction.
哦，拜托，别告诉我你们正带着一个大规模杀伤武器玩坠机把戏

1336
01:41:18,137 --> 01:41:19,872
No, Frank, no.
不，弗兰克，不要啊

1337
01:41:25,645 --> 01:41:26,945
Oh, God.
哦，我的天啊

1338
01:41:39,926 --> 01:41:41,360
You okay back there, Marvin?
你还好吗，马文？

1339
01:41:41,362 --> 01:41:44,663
It wasn't exactly a three-point landing, Frank.
这次着陆可真不咋样，弗兰克

1340
01:41:44,665 --> 01:41:45,931
How's the bomb doing?
炸弹怎样了？

1341
01:41:49,269 --> 01:41:50,636
I can't stop it.
我没法让它停止

1342
01:42:04,550 --> 01:42:06,051
We gotta get it outta here.
我们要赶紧带它离开这里

1343
01:42:07,620 --> 01:42:09,421
Hey! Hey!
嘿！嘿！

1344
01:42:09,423 --> 01:42:10,522
Get outta the car.
从车里出来

1345
01:42:22,535 --> 01:42:24,336
Hello, Frank.
你好，弗兰克

1346
01:42:24,338 --> 01:42:25,337
Welcome aboard.
欢迎登机

1347
01:42:28,508 --> 01:42:30,442
Always the good soldier, aren't you?
始终是个忠诚的战士，是不？

1348
01:42:32,312 --> 01:42:34,079
Stalemate.
现在成了僵局

1349
01:42:34,081 --> 01:42:37,950
How will you take him out and not shoot her first?
你该怎么只打死他而不伤到她呢？

1350
01:42:39,686 --> 01:42:42,721
Frank, it's okay.
弗兰克，没事的

1351
01:42:42,723 --> 01:42:44,690
You can shoot. It's okay.
你开枪吧 没事的

1352
01:42:46,092 --> 01:42:48,961
Put the gun down.
放下枪

1353
01:42:49,996 --> 01:42:50,963
Put the gun down!
放下枪！

1354
01:42:53,266 --> 01:42:54,599
Drop the gun!
把枪扔了！

1355
01:42:57,570 --> 01:43:01,039
Put the gun down, Frankie.
把枪放下，弗兰克

1356
01:43:02,275 --> 01:43:03,508
Thank you.
谢谢你

1357
01:43:04,978 --> 01:43:06,178
Pretty smart.
真机灵

1358
01:43:07,680 --> 01:43:10,382
So love does conquer all.
于是爱情战胜了一切

1359
01:43:11,584 --> 01:43:13,251
Go to your golden warrior.
到你的黄金圣斗士身边去吧

1360
01:43:16,155 --> 01:43:17,055
That's a good girl.
真是个好姑娘

1361
01:43:19,292 --> 01:43:20,392
Aw!
啊！

1362
01:43:23,296 --> 01:43:24,563
Come here.
来抱抱

1363
01:43:24,565 --> 01:43:27,165
Ah! It's so sweet.
啊！真甜蜜

1364
01:43:29,068 --> 01:43:32,604
Now leave the plane. Take Nightshade with you.
现在离开飞机，顺便带上夜暮

1365
01:43:34,607 --> 01:43:35,741
Bye, Frank.
再见，弗兰克

1366
01:43:38,244 --> 01:43:39,511
Sweet dreams.
祝好梦

1367
01:43:55,728 --> 01:43:57,429
Why didn't you just shoot me?
为什么你不直接开枪打我？

1368
01:44:16,315 --> 01:44:18,750
- What happened? - I couldn't disarm it.
怎么了？我没能拆除炸弹

1369
01:44:27,060 --> 01:44:28,560
Oh, crap.
哦，要死了

1370
01:44:30,397 --> 01:44:31,797
Marvin,
马文

1371
01:44:31,799 --> 01:44:33,632
it's going to detonate?
就要爆炸了吗？

1372
01:44:33,634 --> 01:44:35,133
Yeah.
是啊

1373
01:44:35,135 --> 01:44:36,168
Put your arms around me.
抱住我

1374
01:44:59,392 --> 01:45:00,559
Oh...
哦...

1375
01:45:02,395 --> 01:45:03,762
I didn't see that one coming.
我可没想到有这一招

1376
01:45:23,316 --> 01:45:25,417
There's something you don't see every day.
这个奇景可不是每天都能见到的

1377
01:45:31,157 --> 01:45:32,557
You put the bomb on the plane.
你把炸弹放到了飞机上

1378
01:45:36,395 --> 01:45:39,698
And, um, you didn't think to mention that?
那个，嗯，你也不准备通知咱一声？

1379
01:45:39,700 --> 01:45:41,633
You blew up my plane.
你居然把我的飞机给炸了

1380
01:45:41,635 --> 01:45:43,235
Sorry.
对不起

1381
01:45:43,237 --> 01:45:45,437
I was wrong? So we're not even gonna die?
我搞错了？就是说我们都不会死喽？

1382
01:45:46,439 --> 01:45:47,539
Not yet.
还没呢

1383
01:45:49,208 --> 01:45:53,478
I was actually starting to like you. I was even thinking about not killing you.
我确实开始喜欢你了。我甚至在考虑不杀你

1384
01:45:53,480 --> 01:45:55,714
This is what happens when you try to save the world.
